{"tid":670646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[賊喊捉賊]潘樂陶指電梯意外頻生　若處理不當或激發社會矛盾問題","createTime":"2018-05-19T14:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T16:03:00.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"68437eb25ea3c210363ab2fa88e655438cd96efa","tid":670646,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T14:19:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1397198-20180519.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1397198-20180519.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=U71G0TWnB5URXsXGsVz6tU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=ca2da878\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1397198-20180519.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4a697e61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1397198-20180519.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n升降機及自動梯安全諮詢委員會主席潘樂陶在本台節目《香港家書》表示，近年電梯和扶手電梯意外頻生，為社會和業界敲響了警鐘，認為若處理不當，可能激發為社會矛盾問題。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，香港7萬多台電梯及電扶梯，有一半機齡為20年以上，三成是30年以上，應該更換不符合現代安全規格的電梯。他又指，很多大廈立案法團都以「價低者得」形式，委托電梯承辦商維修保養，令質素下降。<br />\n<br />\n他建議提高從業員的工資和待遇，以吸引新人入行，認為電梯公司不應只做例行維修工作，「頭痛醫頭，腳痛醫腳」，亦要做好預測性保養工作。<br />\n<br />\n他鼓勵立案法團參考機電工程署提供的註冊承辦商服務表現評級，以及私人住宅樓宇升降機的保養價格數據，以選擇電梯維修承辦商。政府可考慮提供資助或低息貸款予有需要的立案法團，幫助居民早日大修或更換電梯。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，政府你自己帶頭價賤者得，睇下龜鐵，機場，政府建築物全部都比雜廠雜晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81b7a6e6c81f67e6c5c9818a408c20cbf4df96b6","tid":670646,"uid":14908,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:20:18.000Z","msg":"潘樂陶叫你間atal加人工先啦"},{"pid":"c1b7e995e8b947d4baba9dc0b680dd2db02b781e","tid":670646,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊個老公？"},{"pid":"8e62574726f83f8b03fe64e71f6a7beb5be7e049","tid":670646,"uid":85685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:44:00.000Z","msg":"邊個會理"},{"pid":"a2c2502ef738136e00b2dfc227447ca3a0586deb","tid":670646,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1b7e995e8b947d4baba9dc0b680dd2db02b781e","tid":670646,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊個老公？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"就係佢<br />\n有間機電工程公司準備上市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ce4cd6793a79bbc850153fcbc03d3413776102","tid":670646,"uid":182192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1b7e995e8b947d4baba9dc0b680dd2db02b781e","tid":670646,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊個老公？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T16:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}